## WORDPRESS AND AMAZON WEB SERVICES NOTES ##

THE INTERNET WORKS LIKE THIS:

MY PC --> FTP CLIENT --> WEB SERVER --> THE WIRE --> THE SERVER WHERE MY STUFF IS --> ANY PC THAT KNOWS THE URL

WORDPRESS | FILEZILLA | APACHE | DECODES THE URL INTO THE IP ADDRESS AND SHOWS THE WEBSITE
