BUT ITS A HELL LOT EASIER TO USE THE AMAZON RDS TO SETUP A DATABASE

mysql -h <endpoint> -P 3306 -u <mymasteruser> -p
mysql -h <endpoint> -P 3306 -u <mymasteruser> -p
mysql -h myinstance.123456789012.us-east-1.rds.amazonaws.com -P 3306 -u mymasteruser -p

mysql -h mydatabase.cxkbho08zmrj.us-west-2.rds.amazonaws.com -P 3306 -u andralvDB -p

