WORDPRESS !

posts --> they change, like news or blog entries
pages --> static, like forms or a header

press this button --> like a stumbleupon
adding content --> there are editors, its too easy
add media button --> import stuff

adding users --> administrator, editor, user
if you delete an user you delete all of this lil niggas stuff

theme editor tab --> 'expert' stuff. not recommended. 
use 'resize thumbnails' plugin if images dont fit my theme

appearance --> customize -> do stuff
widgets --> javascript stuff

appearance --> widgets
appearance --> menus -> drag and drop -> can nest menus

theme providers: iThemes, WooThemes, themeforest




